Detailed Description

cvmx_mdab::_wr_addr

The starting address used by the WR-DMA engine when reading WR-DMA data from local DSP memory. During Job_Type = ST_LCL* commands, hardware loads the WR_ADDR/WR_LIMIT registers directly.
